hopobject.body: perfect design thanks www.my-pharm.de Somebody rendered paraplegic or quadriplegic by the crash, says Danko, could expect (from a U.S. court) compensation of $5 million to $10 million. There were passengers who sustained spinal cord injuries, he says, but doctors have yet to determine whether any of these will result in partial or complete paralysis. In Germany, he says, rewards for such injuries are capped at $400,000 to $500,000.
